      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "person or organization (esp. yakuza) in charge of solving problems caused by subordinates",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "あの組織は強力なケツ持ちがいるから、誰も手出しできない。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "トラブルが起きたとき、誰がケツ持ちしてくれるのかが重要だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼は町内の揉め事を解決する、頼れるケツ持ち役だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "member of a biker gang driving behind the rest (in charge of keeping the police away from the other members)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "ツーリングでは、一番後ろを走るケツ持ちが全体の安全を見守る。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "ケツ持ちのベテランライダーが、新人たちを指導した。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "隊列のケツ持ちは、後続車両との距離を保つ役割がある。",
